      ,[IsHistoricalFileLoaded]
      ,[IsCompleteLoad]

      ,[CSIDatabaseName]

Select t1.*
FROM [DW].[dim_invoice_number] t1
join dw.fact_invoice_trans t2 on t1.invoice_number_key=t2.invoice_number_key
join dw.stage_club_RCM t3 on t2.club_key=t3.Club_Key
---where source_key = 2

source.sqlReaderQuery:
select 
item_key,
item_text_key,
item_id,
item_version,
item_name,
item_desc,
item_frequency,
item_duration_desc,
item_dept_name,
item_profit_center_name,
item_category_cd,
item_category_name,
item_category_desc,
item_category_status,
item_location_id,
item_location_name,
item_type,
item_expiration_start_desc,
item_expiration_time_unit_desc,
item_expiration_time_unit_cnt,
item_quantity,
item_quantity_range,
item_price_amt,
item_price_range,
item_unlimited_flg,
item_active_flg,
item_actual_flg,
item_service_flg,
item_created_utc_date,
item_deactivated_utc_date,
CAST (deactivated_flag AS DECIMAL (1,0)) AS deactivated_flag,
source_key,
source_change_date,
data_warehouse_change_date,
effective_date,
expiration_date,
CAST (current_flag AS DECIMAL (1,0)) AS current_flag
 from dw.dim_item t1
join [DW].[stage_club_RCM] t2 on t1.item_location_id=t2.loc_id
---where source_key =2

SELECT m.[MemberKey]
      ,[MemberType]
      ,[addressLine1]
      ,[barcode]
      ,[birthDate]
      ,[city]
      ,[countryCode]
      ,[createdTimestamp]
      ,[email]
      ,[firstCheckInTimestamp]
      ,[firstName]
      ,[FitBiDateCreatedUTC]
      ,[FitBiDateModifiedUTC]
      ,m.[Club_Key]
      ,[gender]
      ,'UN' AS "group1"
	  ,CASE when [hasPhoto] = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS [hasPhoto]
      ,[homeClub]
      ,[insert_dt]
      ,CASE when [isActive] = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS [isActive]
      ,CASE when [isConvertedProspect] = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS [isConvertedProspect]
      ,[joinStatus]
      ,[lastCheckInTimestamp]
      ,[lastName]
      ,[Id]
      ,[Status]
      ,[StatusDate]
      ,[StatusReason]
      ,[personal]
      ,[postalCode]
      ,[state]
      ,[totalCheckInCount]
      ,[agreementEntrySource]
      ,[agreementEntrySourceReportName]
      ,[beginDate]
      ,[campaignkey]
      ,[expirationDate]
      ,[issueDate]
      ,[leadPriority]
      ,[locationState]
      ,[middleInitial]
      ,[misc1]
      ,[misc2]
      ,[primaryPhone]
      ,[referringMemberKey]
      ,[salesPersonKey]
      ,[tourDate]
      ,[visitsAllowed]
      ,[visitsUsed]
      ,[workPhone]
      ,[record_eff_from_dt]
      ,[record_eff_to_dt]
      ,[commissionLevel]
      ,[startDate]
      ,[terminationDate]
      ,[trainingLevel]
      ,[wage]
      ,[HomePhone]
      ,[CellPhone]
      ,[Prospect_Key]
      ,[EmergencyAvailability]
      ,[Emergencyext]
      ,[EmergencyPhone]
      ,[Age_Class]
      ,[AllCareNum]
      ,[WellnessProgramID]
      ,CASE when [FitBiMemberActive] = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS [FitBiMemberActive]
      ,m.[vpd_id]
      ,[insertDt]
      ,[ModifiedDt]
      ,[memberCd]
      ,m.[source_key]
  FROM [DimFact].[DimMember] m
  join [DW].[stage_club_RCM] t2 on m.Club_key=t2.Club_Key
  join dw.fact_invoice_trans inv on m.MemberKey=inv.member_key
--where inv.source_key=2
